OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FSouth East Water's under-fire chief
OL,8,Fexecutive has refused to appear before
OL,9,Fa council scrutiny committee
OL,10,Finvestigating recent major supply
OL,11,Ffailures in Tunbridge Wells.
OL,13,FIn a letter, obtained by ITV News
OL,14,FMeridian, David Hinton tells Tunbridge
OL,15,FWells Borough Council's head of
OL,16,Fgovernance that he feels the meeting
OL,17,Fis "happening too soon" for him to be
OL,18,Fable to give the committee "the
OL,19,Fanswers they understandably want".
