OL,3,CSouth East Water chief executive
OL,4,Crefuses to attend council scrutiny
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FThe CEO has faced mounting calls to
OL,8,Fresign over recent weeks, with several
OL,9,FMPs and council leaders saying he
OL,10,Fshould step down or be sacked.
OL,12,FIn response to the latest revelation,
OL,13,FTunbridge Wells Liberal Democrat MP
OL,14,FMike Martin said: "South East Water is
OL,15,Fonce again hiding from accountability.
OL,17,F"But if they think for one second that
OL,18,FI'm going to let them get away with
OL,19,Fsuch brazen contempt for the people of
OL,20,FTunbridge Wells, then they've got
OL,21,Fanother thing coming".
