OL,7,FTunbridge Wells Borough Council's
OL,8,Foverview and scrutiny committee had
OL,9,Frequested the attendance of David
OL,10,FHinton at its meeting on Monday, 26
OL,11,FJanuary.
OL,13,FThe letter from Mr Hinton - dated 22
OL,14,FJanuary - is titled "Postponement of
OL,15,Fattendance at Overview and Scrutiny
OL,16,FCommittee".
