OL,4,Crefuses to attend council scrutiny
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,FThe chief executive writes: "Given how
OL,8,Frecent the latest supply interruptions
OL,9,Fare, we are still in the early stages
OL,10,Fof our own internal investigation into
OL,11,Fthe incident.
OL,13,F"As such, we are not in a position to
OL,14,Fdraw any firm conclusions and provide
OL,15,Fthe level of detail we feel is
OL,16,Fnecessary to fully satisfy the
OL,17,Fcommittee.
