OL,4,Crefuses to attend council scrutiny
OL,5,Cmeeting
OL,7,F"I am very sorry for the inconvenience
OL,8,Fthis causes...I want to reassure you
OL,9,Fthat we are committed to having this
OL,10,Fin-person meeting."
OL,12,FWater supplies returned this week to
OL,13,Fthe remaining properties in Kent after
OL,14,Fmore than a week of disruption.
OL,16,FAt the height of the incident, which
OL,17,Fbegan on 10 January, SEW said more
OL,18,Fthan 30,000 customers across Kent and
OL,19,FSussex were without water or
OL,20,Fexperiencing low water pressure.
